cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.SE 

The paper discusses formal methods for reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses safety-critical settings, which suggests that it may belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence and Robotics) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). The use of deductive proving and design-time model updates suggests that it may also belong to cs.SE (Software Engineering). Finally, the paper discusses optimization, which suggests that it may belong to cs.RO (Robotics and Automation).
